data.description: Ideal multi-generational 5 bedroom and 3 FULL bath home, designed with functionality in mind. The main level has both a Primary bedroom/en suite bathroom and a Guest bedroom with full secondary bathroom just steps away. The Kitchen has an abundance of storage, 42 inch dark wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances including double ovens and oversized breakfast bar. The combined living, dining and kitchen area is perfect for gatherings. Just up the stairs is a spacious game room/flex space and three additional bedrooms. Updates include recent roof replacement (2 years) and AC unit (< 1 year). Easy access to tons of shopping, dining, and entertainment including The Crossover, Lakewood Park, HEB Center and more.
